        <li>Responds to enquiries and emails in a timely and responsive manner;</li>
        <li>Work closely and flexibly with colleagues in a small team;</li>
        <li>Manage the “catch all” admin@streetsupport.net email address;</li>
        <li>Participate in management and all-staff meetings; and</li>
        <li>Other duties as assigned.</li>
